[00:39.09]	[Enter JULIET]
[00:39.79]CAPULET	How now, my headstrong! where have you been gadding?
[00:43.03]JULIET	Where I have learn'd me to repent the sin
[00:45.81]	Of disobedient opposition
[00:47.66]	To you and your behests, and am enjoin'd
[00:50.33]	By holy Laurence to fall prostrate here,
[00:52.99]	And beg your pardon: pardon, I beseech you!
[00:55.71]	Henceforward I am ever ruled by you.
