[01:09.15]	Not step o'er the bounds of modesty.
[01:11.58]CAPULET	Why, I am glad on't; this is well: stand up:
[01:14.30]	This is as't should be. Let me see the county;
[01:17.26]	Ay, marry, go, I say, and fetch him hither.
[01:19.86]	Now, afore God! this reverend holy friar,
